OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776449465
OL,3,CElectrician's 'livelihood in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cafter #10,000 of tools stolen from van
OL,6,FAn electrician from Farnborough says
OL,7,Fhis livelihood is in jeopardy after
OL,8,Ftools worth around #10,000 were stolen
OL,9,Ffrom his van.
OL,11,FThieves took the equipment from his
OL,12,Fvehicle which was parked in a
OL,13,FMorrison's supermarket yesterday
OL,14,Fmorning.
OL,16,FIt's also affected his ability to
OL,17,Fteach his apprentice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
