OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776449465
OL,3,CElectrician's 'livelihood in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cafter #10,000 of tools stolen from van
OL,6,FGroups representing tradespeople is
OL,7,Fcalling for tougher legislation to
OL,8,Fprotect them from thefts- including
OL,9,Frequiring manufacturers to put
OL,10,Fforensic markings on power tools.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Liam
OL,13,FShepherd described arriving to his van
OL,14,Fand discovering the doors open with
OL,15,Fthings all over the floor.
OL,17,F"It was gut-wrenching to be honest,"
OL,18,Fhe said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776449465
OL,3,CElectrician's 'livelihood in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cafter #10,000 of tools stolen from van
OL,6,F"We had pretty much 80% of our tools
OL,7,Fin there. We'd invested in some test
OL,8,Fequipment that we use on the bigger
OL,9,Fjobs, and that was gone.
OL,11,F"We needed to finish a job yesterday,
OL,12,Fbut we couldn't finish the job because
OL,13,Fwe couldn't test it."
OL,15,FPolice say that they are committed to
OL,16,Fcracking down on tool theft but Liam
OL,17,Fsays they followed security guidance
OL,18,Fand were still targeted.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776449465
OL,3,CElectrician's 'livelihood in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cafter #10,000 of tools stolen from van
OL,6,F"We've got van security, we've got
OL,7,Fsort of the hook locks, the dead
OL,8,Fshields, as they call them, that are
OL,9,Fmeant to be a deterrent parked in a
OL,10,Fsecure car park," Liam added.
OL,12,F"It was in broad daylight next to the
OL,13,Fstreet.
OL,15,F"There's nothing more we could have
OL,16,Fdone apart from not have any tools.
OL,18,F"That tool for us is our livelihood
OL,19,Fand thousands of pounds, which they're
OL,20,Fstolen in seconds and sold for
OL,21,Fpittance and what they're worth.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776449465
OL,3,CElectrician's 'livelihood in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cafter #10,000 of tools stolen from van
OL,6,F"For us, that's a day-to-day what we
OL,7,Fneed. I've got a young family - that
OL,8,Fcould have been me out of a job."
OL,10,FApprentice Charlie Cookman had built
OL,11,Fup his tools while studying his
OL,12,Fapprenticeship and says the theft has
OL,13,Fleft him "devastated."
OL,15,F"There's things that, I guess, you can
OL,16,Fput in place, like taking only the
OL,17,Ftools that you need," he said.
OL,19,F"But at the end of the day, you
OL,20,Fshouldn't be having to do that.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776449465
OL,3,CElectrician's 'livelihood in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cafter #10,000 of tools stolen from van
OL,6,F"I think that's a bigger problem."
OL,8,FLiam said the theft will cause a
OL,9,F"snowball effect" on their larger jobs.
OL,11,F"We've got to go to work and do what
OL,12,Fwe can," he added.
OL,14,F"We can't let our clients down."
OL,16,FThe Home Office says its working with
OL,17,Fpolice to understand where and how
OL,18,Ftools are sold while examining ways to
OL,19,Fensure tools are identifiable and
OL,20,Ftraceable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
