OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776449465
OL,3,CElectrician's 'livelihood in jeopardy'
OL,4,Cafter #10,000 of tools stolen from van
OL,6,FA Met Police spokesperson: "We know
OL,7,Ftoo many tradespeople are being left
OL,8,Fout of work and pocked by organised
OL,9,Fcriminals, which is why we're
OL,10,Fcommitted to cracking down on tool
OL,11,Ftheft.
OL,13,F"Police received a report on Thursday,
OL,14,F16 April that a number of tools had
OL,15,Fbeen stolen from a van in a car park
OL,16,Fon The Grove, Stratford, earlier that
OL,17,Fday, between 09:50hrs and 10:10hrs. No
OL,18,Farrests have been made at this time."
